
Always remember
1.if you create or any existing repo should contain .git to maintain always its history separately
2.you have many repos in github then no worries 
i. create a folder on local
ii.navigate to that folder in linux terminal and use git clone {URL}
iii. finish

3. when you create branch they exist in .git and once you merged to main , branch will automatically delete , you can see the branch commit id in history
use git log --all --decorate --oneline

Commit = actual work/history
Branch = pointer to commits
